<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
    <% include ../partials/head.ejs %>
</head>
<body>
<% include ../partials/error-alert.ejs %>
<div class="container text-center">
    <a href="/"><img class="img-logo" src="images/logo.jpg" alt=""></a>
    <h3>登录</h3>
    <div class="sign-in-sign-up-content row">
        <div id="box-sign-in" class="col-sm-offset-1 col-md-offset-2 col-sm-5 col-md-4 text-left">
            <form action="/sign-in" method="POST">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">电子邮箱</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" placeholder="">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="password">登录密码</label>
                    <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" name="password" placeholder="">
                </div>
                <button id="btn-sign-in" type="submit" class="btn btn-default">登录</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div id="box-third-party-sign-in" class="col-sm-5 col-md-4">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-md btn-block btn-third-party-login">微信登录</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger btn-md btn-block btn-third-party-login">微博登录</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-md btn-block btn-third-party-login">QQ登录</button>
            <p class="text-left text-muted text-sign-in-prompt">通过微信、微博、QQ账号授权，一键快速登录内涵吧</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p>不是会员？<a href="/sign-up">赶紧注册吧!</a></p>
</div>

</body>
</html>